To install mpcrouter on your computer, first install all the runtime dependencies:
$ sudo apt-get install libnss3-tools mkcert ruby-rubygems rubygems-integration ruby-rack ruby-sinatra ruby-sinatra-contrib puma ruby-rack-ssl
$ sudo gem install ruby-dbus
$ sudo make install

Building Debian Packages
==============
To build a debian package, first install all build dependencies, then make the deb-pkg target:
$ sudo apt-get install dh-make devscripts
$ sudo make deb-pkg
